---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-hero-title">About Me</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-description">The person behind the profile</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-card">
        <h2 class="about-card-title">Beyond the Screen</h2>

        <div class="about-content">
          <p>
            Hailing from the quiet town of Etukur in Guntur, Andhra Pradesh, I
            carry the true spirit of a middle-class boy&mdash;grounded, resilient,
            and unapologetically real. Beyond the professional hustle, I'm a
            simple, cool guy who believes that life is best measured by the happy
            moments and the people you share them with.
          </p>

          <p>
            My family is my ultimate anchor; there is nothing better than the
            quiet comfort, laughter, and grounding conversations back home. On
            the flip side, my friends are my absolute fuel. From spontaneous
            roadside tea chats to running the campus like we owned it, making
            memories and sharing laughs with the boys is what keeps life vibrant.
          </p>

          <p>
            No pretense, no fluff&mdash;just a small-town dreamer navigating life
            with a sharp sense of style, casual confidence, and a tight-knit
            circle.
          </p>

          <div class="quote">
            <p class="quote-text">"Life is best measured by the happy moments and the people you share them with."</p>
            <p class="quote-author">&mdash; Jagadeesh</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">1</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Project Built</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">5+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Technologies</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">1+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Years Experience</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">7.5</div>
          <div class="stat-label">MCA CGPA</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
